      "span_text": "The producer cells were able to generate up to 3.4 × 10 7 TU/ml after transducing the packaging cells with a cSIN-LV expressing GFP transgene. Nevertheless, although the very encouraging results obtained with the GFP marker gene, these cells never reached the clinical study stage."
